travel_completed` after fuel is consumed — add logging if needed.\\n- Check whether closing the panel before `initiate_travel()` (the wave 2 reorder) affects any node references or signal connections that TravelSequenceManager relies on.\\n- Confirm the TravelSequenceManager node is present in the scene tree and its `_on_travel_completed` handler is connected at the time travel is initiated.\\n- Look for any `await` that could silently stall (e.g., `await get_tree().create_timer(0).timeout` racing with a freed node).\\n\\nAcceptance criteria (all must be met before marking DONE):\\n- Pressing CONFIRM TRAVEL triggers a visible biome transition (fade out → scene load → fade in).\\n- Player inputs are re-enabled after the transition completes (not before).\\n- The selected biome loads correctly.\\n- All existing unit tests pass.\\n- This ticket has a hold condition requiring Studio Head sign-off — do NOT mark DONE; instead, leave a detailed activity log entry confirming all criteria are met and state 'READY FOR STUDIO HEAD SIGN-OFF'.\"}]}","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"332bfb8d-9e66-4b23-8708-d7c9ef07615c","total_cost_usd":0.2619175,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":20504,"cache_read_input_tokens":135725,"output_tokens":2635,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":20504,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":6,"outputTokens":2635,"cacheReadInputTokens":135725,"cacheCreationInputTokens":20504,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.2619175,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"9632bfed-b17a-4d20-b4dd-bd47d8909696"}]

